NG0797:426: dmar dkri / spyang thod skyes bur bsam /

NG0797:433: mkhon la gzab pa dang lnga */

NG0797:436: stan drod ma yal ba mi la mi 'ding ba @#//

NG0797:444: gdod nas ma skyes rang bzhin dag pa'i sku //
NG0797:445: mnyam nyid rig pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:446: ston pa shakya thub pa'i bstan pa la //
NG0797:447: bstan pa bsrung zhing legs nyes stang 'dzin pa'i //
NG0797:448: dge bsnyen chen po rdo rje legs pa ste //
NG0797:449: 'jig rten skyong ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NG0797:450: khyod ni yab yum dmu bdud bshos pa'i sras //
NG0797:451: bdun tshigs mtha' ru spyugs pas sangs rgyas chos dang mjal //
NG0797:452: lha mi kun gyis dbang bskur rdzu 'phrul can //
NG0797:453: chos byed dam nyams mna' zan rnams kyi gshed //
NG0797:454: skye bo'i dgra lha dgra bo'i gshed ma zhes //
NG0797:455: gzhan gyi ma bcos nyid kyi zhal bzhes pa //
NG0797:456: legs nyes stang 'dzin khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:457: don dam nges pa'i bden pa ma mthong yang *//
NG0797:458: skyes mchog khyad par can gyi gang zag gis //
NG0797:459: dbang bskur ming btags las kyi gnyer gtad pa //
NG0797:460: chos skyong srungs ma khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:461: rang gis las dang bsod nams rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NG0797:462: lho yi 'dzam gling khyab cing kun tu rgyu /
NG0797:463: khyad par bzhugs pa'i bod yul yongs kyis spel //
NG0797:464: yul lha gnyan po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:465: sngon tshe thog ma rang gi bag chags bsam //
NG0797:466: smon lam dam bca' nyid kyi mos pa yis //
NG0797:467: rgya bod gtsang bgrod pa yi sna 'dren pa //
NG0797:468: tshong dpon chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:469: skye bo 'thab rtsod g.yul chen sprod pa'i tshe //
NG0797:470: gang zhig khyod la gsol mchod byed pa des //
NG0797:471: dmag gi ru bzlog pha rol g.yul 'joms pa //
NG0797:472: dmag dpon chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:473: 'jig rten 'di na lta ba log pa yi //
NG0797:474: mu stegs bon smra thog par bsten pa dang *//
NG0797:475: de dang mthun par 'jig rten skyong mdzad pa //
NG0797:476: thun mong lha mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:477: 'jig rten 'di na mthu che gang yod kyang *//
NG0797:478: bcol ba'i las rnams myur du mi 'grub ste /
NG0797:479: khyod ni bdag gi rten cing las bcol lo //
NG0797:480: myur du grub byed khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:481: 'khor ba'i gnas na lha srin gzhan rten yang *//
NG0797:482: dgra rnams gsod kyang bdag la gnod par 'gyur /
NG0797:483: khyod ni gang dang 'dris na rtag tu skyobs //
NG0797:484: yum gyi mgon mdzad khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0797:485: 'jig rten 'di na ma mchog gzhan rten yang *//
NG0797:486: zug rngu drag cing rtogs pa rab tu che /
NG0797:487: khyod ni mi nag skye bos bsgrub na yang *//
NG0797:488: mthu dbang ster byed khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NG0797:489: khyod ni gsang sngags dam tshig can //
NG0797:490: bdag kyang dam srung dam tshig mnyan por bsrungs //

NG0797:493: don dam mtshungs pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:494: spyir na nyid kyi mthu dang rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NG0797:495: sku mdog phyag mtshan gcig tu ma nges te //
NG0797:496: sngags kyi phyag mtshan phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NG0797:497: rdo rje legs pa khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //

NG0797:499: ra sha khrag tshil rtag tu zas su gsol //
NG0797:500: ra yi pags pa nyid kyang na bzar gsol //
NG0797:501: skyes bu rdzu 'phrul can la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:502: spyir ni nyid kyi mthu dang rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NG0797:503: gcig tu ma nges gnas skabs tha dad kyang *//
NG0797:504: bka' dang bstan pa bsrungs bar zhal bzhes pa //
NG0797:505: gtsug lag dben gnas bsrung la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:506: dad pa'i yid kyis gdung pa'i skyems phyung nas //
NG0797:507: gus shing dad pas lus ngag sems btud nas //
NG0797:508: yon tan ri rab snyed las rdul tsam zhig / dad pas dad gus phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:509: kun bzang thabs kyis sku la khyad sprul nas /
NG0797:510: bdud rje brgya dang mtshungs par mthu bo che //
NG0797:511: lag nas thog 'bebs kha nas ser chen skyug / thog ser skyin thang 'bebs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:512: gsang ba'i gying chen bco brgyad kyis //
NG0797:513: mnga' bdag chen po gzi 'bar rtsal //
NG0797:514: stag smad sum brgya drug cu'i 'khor gyi gtso bo mdzad //
NG0797:515: srog dbugs mdangs la dbang byed pa'i //
NG0797:516: dgra sdang srog gcod khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0797:517: rgyal ba'i bka' dang shakya thub pa'i gsung *//
NG0797:518: las bcol gnyer gtad bka' bzhin bstan pa bsrungs //

NG0797:522: lha srin phyag brnyan 'gyed cing sprul pa pho nyar gtong *//
NG0797:523: gnam sa ri lung bar snang sprul pas 'gengs //

NG0797:525: 'jigs pa'i gzugs can rdo rje legs pa khyod //

NG0797:528: rnal 'byor dkor rnams bsrung la phyag 'tshal bstod //

NG0797:531: gnod sbyin rdo rje stag mda'i rgyud las /
